# Cloudflare Pages redirects — https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
# Format: <source> <destination> <status>

# Force the apex domain as canonical. Requires www.monopoly-repo.dev to be
# attached as a custom domain on this Pages project, otherwise the request
# never reaches Pages and this rule won't fire.
https://www.monopoly-repo.dev/* https://monopoly-repo.dev/:splat 301
